  with analysis of the Organised Crime Investment Portfolio;</b></font><!--mstheme--></font><!--msthemelist--></td></tr>
  <!--msthemelist--><tr><td valign="baseline" width="42"><img src="_themes/breeze/bull1_breeze.gif" width="11" height="13" hspace="15" alt="bullet"></td><td valign="top" width="100%"><!--mstheme--><font face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><font size="1"><b>the Victorian dept of Justice with a workload and 
