von Braun</span></a></p>
<p ALIGN="JUSTIFY" STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm">
<font face="Bradley Hand ITC" size="5"><span style="line-height: 115%">It's so 
much easier to suggest solutions when you don't know too much about the problem.</span></font><font size="2"><i> 
-- </i>Malcolm Forbes</font></p>
