<img border="0" src="dt070403.jpg" width="687" height="231"></p>
<p ALIGN="JUSTIFY" STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-top:0"><font size="1">
COPYRIGHT: UNITED FEATURES SYNDICATE INC. Distributed by Auspac Media</font></p>
