  <h3><a href="/media/blog.html">CrimBrief</a></h3>
 <div> <p>The Official Blog of the AIC</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/media/blog.html"><strong>AIC celebrates the JV Barry Librarys 40th Birthday</strong></a></li>
  </ul>
      </div>
